{"tid":883690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★張建宗：不排除直接向美國(Trump)提出磋商！！","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T11:30:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcbe59b78e5a19d1fb1b17e73ed0c73e2eae11d","tid":883690,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"署理行政長官張建宗表示，貿易戰沒有贏家，期望各方能透過雙邊洽談及世貿機制處理貿易糾紛，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">不排除直接向美國提出磋商要求</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他出席灼見名家周年論壇致詞時指，香港今年上半年受惠於環球經濟，經濟增長強勁，第三季經濟穩定擴張，不過好景不常，美國推出貿易保護措施，令自由化進程大倒退。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗說，中美貿易戰將惡化，香港將受一定波及，承受顯著的直接及間接的影響，不能獨善其身。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，美國加息、英國脫歐及中東政局不穩等，增添不穩因素，特區政府會密切留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425782-20181031.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425782-20181031.htm&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7e37be03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1425782-20181031.htm&h=3d2a4c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1425782-20181031.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ae92dd40cc32f90b0d0a0d338f265865624a4918","tid":883690,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b1cccb33a82bd8423ad8a5fad28a6497b08e72","tid":883690,"uid":171107,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"你老幾"},{"pid":"97ffe2bc4575a5c572a5d85ba1b3df60a8e1e285","tid":883690,"uid":759,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:37:17.000Z","msg"